LORE rakuen-warden
FLAGS RAKUEN GUARD
Ember Wardens: disaster-response corps; function as de facto law enforcement;
their emergency adjudication bench operates outside normal circle mediation
Labor drafts during active disaster conditions are authorized under emergency
law; Ember Wardens enforce them; politically contested but legally valid
Route security through the Eccentric Woodland managed by path-guides under
Ember Warden contract; no formal road warden presence on Rakuen approaches
The Wardens claim Orn Fallsbridge (site-selector, first boundary-staker)
as their institutional ancestor; the oath: "I walk where Fallsbridge walked,
and I do not flinch at what he found."
Ration tower access controlled by Ember Wardens during shortage declarations;
this is classified as "welfare infrastructure" not fortification
Kiess Temple delegates observe Ember Warden labor draft procedures for
charter-compliance review; this is an ongoing tension
~
